Helm installation
------------------
Installing Helm  #https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/
	$ curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/main/scripts/get-helm-3 | bash
Adding a repo
	$ helm repo add stable https //kubernetes-charts.storage.googleapis.com
List the added repo
	$ helm repo list
Fetch the latest state of the repo
	$ helm repo update
To know what is inside the repo
	$ helm search repo 
Install a chat
	$ helm install redis-test stable/redis 
	$ kubectl get pod
	$ helm ls
To Uninstall 
	$ helm unistall redis-test
